{"tid":1476353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"見到有冷血軍師吹風話帶gear會嚇走和理非","createTime":"2019-08-15T19:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T05:36:05.000Z","uid":43785,"like":81,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c39e7b1793c674949fa0a8c3a6c4fc7c9e8a506a","tid":1476353,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:26:20.000Z","msg":"見到有冷血軍師吹風話帶gear會嚇走和理非......大佬唔好咁痴線啦！今時今日和平遊行放催淚彈係最低消費，連催淚彈都嚇唔走，反而gear會嚇走？講個條友有冇出過街㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家發唔發覺每次都叫勇武收皮，叫人唔好帶gear，到時放催淚彈嘅時候，嗰啲人全部有份參與謀殺？<br />\n勇武返屋企？機場嗰日冇勇武，個女仔畀人塔返去融撚咗啦！衝唔衝係戰術考慮，叫人唔好衝絕對冇問題，但係叫你連防禦性gear都唔帶嘅人，都好肯定想你死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c19c5c55d0ffbc8345bdb54e90396c8e05639bb","tid":1476353,"uid":43785,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:26:30.000Z","msg":"仲有呀，留唔留意到最近多返咗畀人秋後算帳嘅人？其中一個原因都好肯定係最近多咗人叫大家唔好著黑色衫，唔知嗰啲人想食人血饅頭定乜，大家千祈唔好唔記得blackbloc，唔統一裝束好容易睇cam秋後算帳。"},{"pid":"28349aa14a203b4b805c926adf1427850d877eec","tid":1476353,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:29:25.000Z","msg":"bb早啲瞓啦，唔好捱壞身子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c70e0ce4c0f83f8661b3ed0a4473089236c3876","tid":1476353,"uid":2883,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:30:27.000Z","msg":"佢哋覺得坐喺度比狗咬就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過班冷血軍師有咩事9秒9跑走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f45daaadff3599af40b2f8e53365bbb49bac76e","tid":1