 />\n<br />\n今日d女示威者講， 月經血顏色變咗黑色， d催淚彈好毒架<br />\n<br />\npopo打手係度攪分化， 唔好入真正連登仔既數<br />\n<br />\n唔好再理popo分化打手講既野， 唔好再記住， 唔好放係心<br />\n<br />\n不分化， 死都唔割"},{"pid":"adc9e83009dbefc120a2c49625b641ef057ba8e3","tid":1476353,"uid":58624,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:47:14.000Z","msg":"手足捉到鬼記住用擦唔甩既筆寫8964/京A88 etc<br />\n係佢地身上 整個連儂人"},{"pid":"5de407dd220079e4c6dedd5bce0b73298416d36d","tid":1476353,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adc9e83009dbefc120a2c49625b641ef057ba8e3","tid":1476353,"uid":58624,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:47:14.000Z","msg":"手足捉到鬼記住用擦唔甩既筆寫8964/京A88 etc<br />\n係佢地身上 整個連儂人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:49:23.000Z","msg":"仲玩捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a19347f0c256f26f24814dbe02068e6ef8da2c","tid":1476353,"uid":295889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:50:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認真理性討論post 大家幫手入嚟投票</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Set deadline再升級係大多手足嘅共識 大家一齊去公投同討下啦 要過5,000正評 民間記者會應該要反映到抗爭者主流意見同策略</span> </span><br />\n冇網絡大軍同P牌不能好評 要靠大家！！<br />\n<br />\n【公投】民間記者會設限825通牒林奠答應訴求（係答應唔係回應！！！）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dEHHFS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dEHHFS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"4a5f39236c7b6563a436b9e558596a4f75147008","tid":1476353,"uid":289751,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:53:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得話叫人唔帶gear嗰d。等於叫人攪野唔好帶套,不負責任。其實帶gear有咩問題, 你又唔係主出擊。全部野都無殺傷力, 就話驚嚇親人, 同自我查有咩分別。"},{"pid":"de581a4ae94db0f03b5b3a4af77571a30f5ab885","tid":1476353,"uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T20:04:10.000Z","msg":"大家都well educated<br />\n有句說話明槍易擋唉"